    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/6e6dd829143b40ef74f02cfa0358e63b.avif?t=1734109296\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience Night at the Office, a walking simulator, puzzle horror game focused on placing you into the heart of an environment full of terror, suspense and surprise. Night at the Office focuses on delivering a story-rich murder mystery coupled with many horror elements to make the experience far more exciting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/ad629fdbf2f83c30256086d20b255f4c.avif?t=1734109296\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Joseph Anadam was found at the bottom of the elevator bank at the Emerging Group Lp, a death where nobody yet knows the true cause. It is now nighttime and you are working late at the office trying to get some extra work done. Throughout the night, you begin experiencing headaches and phenomenon which begin to tie many causes to Joseph’s death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who killed Joseph Anadam and why are you the one who is being put through the terrors of uncovering his death?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/0502922bf4a8ad50ae481634c5a4b9d9.poster.avif?t=1734109296\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/0502922bf4a8ad50ae481634c5a4b9d9.webm?t=1734109296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/0502922bf4a8ad50ae481634c5a4b9d9.mp4?t=1734109296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/0cf09ee541faa223338a6bfe45c12a55.avif?t=1734109296\" width=600 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Night at the office is estimated to be completed in 1 hour and offers the following:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          Mid-way checkpoint to allow you to resume or experience multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          3 endings, each revealing a new element to the storyline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          1 Easter Egg, as always…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          Several puzzles of varying difficulty to test your observation and critical thinking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          Multiple achievements to allow you to experience all the game has to offer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/57498e2814d1cd7e3431a75fc5da1a5f.poster.avif?t=1734109296\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/57498e2814d1cd7e3431a75fc5da1a5f.webm?t=1734109296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305350/extras/57498e2814d1cd7e3431a75fc5da1a5f.mp4?t=1734109296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you all for your support. This has been an excellent game to develop after not pushing any new title out for almost 2 years. As always, I am super excited to read your reviews and hear your thoughts on the game once it is released!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stan. T</p>",
